Subject: drm/tve200: Use drm_gem_fb_create() and drm_gem_fb_prepare_fb()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 57b8a4bf87806cbb64ed91078f32fbf37f556c5e
Patch-mainline: v4.15-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

drm_fb_cma_create() and drm_fb_cma_prepare_fb() are just wrappers now,
use drm_gem_fb_create() and drm_gem_fb_prepare_fb() directly.

